column16: Brian Dozier walks.   Aaron Hicks to 3rd.    Eduardo Escobar to 2nd.
Eduardo Escobar hits a sacrifice bunt.   Sam Fuld scores.    Aaron Hicks to 2nd.    Eduardo Escobar to 1st.  Throwing error by catcher Bryan Holaday.
Josmil Pinto grounds out, shortstop Andrew Romine to first baseman Miguel Cabrera.
Chris Colabello pops out to first baseman Miguel Cabrera on the infield fly rule.
Trevor Plouffe hit by pitch.    Joe Mauer to 2nd.
Tigers challenged (tag play), call on the field was overturned: With Joe Mauer batting, Brian Dozier caught stealing 2nd base, catcher Bryan Holaday to shortstop Andrew Romine.
